-- New York Counterterrorism Official Says Vulnerable Spots Will Be Targeted
-- Chris Dolmetsch
-- 2010-06-28T17:20:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/new-york-counterterrorism-official-says-vulnerable-spots-will-be-targeted.html

          
          
             New York Police Department
Counterterrorism Chief Richard Daddario said terrorists will
seek to strike vulnerable locations in New York City in any
future attacks. He spoke today during a conference call from
Moscow.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
